However for many others, there are &quot;hard core&quot; Guilds that exist for these challenges. I think you can agree that LoS is one.<br>
<br>
This doesn't justify their actions, or their excuse for a Guildmaster, but at least I understand their rationale.<br>
<br>
Something to consider before you go forward with this idea...</font><P><FONT COLOR="RED" SIZE="+2" FACE="times new roman">Orogastus<BR>
